{"tid":2429343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"否決預算變顛覆 控方無解釋","createTime":"2021-03-02T08:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T08:43:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c09bc9309fbdf7ab71b90fb59584923162e30c41","tid":2429343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T08:28:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210302/WF2J5OIKNJCJLCK4NV3GKOSHGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210302%2FWF2J5OIKNJCJLCK4NV3GKOSHGU%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=f0861940\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210302%2FWF2J5OIKNJCJLCK4NV3GKOSHGU%2F&h=b7d8d675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210302/WF2J5OIKNJCJLCK4NV3GKOSHGU/</a><br />\n<br />\n否決預算變顛覆 控方無解釋<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】控方匆匆提早起訴47人顛覆國家政權罪，指控他們企圖在立法會奪取大多數議席，藉拒絕通過財政預算引致立法會解散、行政長官辭職，迫使特首回應五大訴求；整個計劃維持七個月，在國安法之後仍繼續，只是受疫情影響，立法會選舉延遲，才令他們未能完成顛覆國家政權陰謀。可是，控方無解釋，打算透過合法選舉取得議席，並且行使職權拒絕通過財政預算，如何構成顛覆國家政權行為，或有何法律理據。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：被告呻肚餓 官准輪流食飯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/L6wjH0i9YIvFE4gfM99_c-851X8=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CCSBE2HITZARVGDQECO4Z53OTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FL6wjH0i9YIvFE4gfM99_c-851X8%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCCSBE2HITZARVGDQECO4Z53OTY.jpg&h=0ab820c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年民主派初選，逾60萬人投票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「罪狀」涵蓋國安立法前<br />\n<br />\n控方詳列國安法立法前。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民主動力為初選提供支援，包括協。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方於今年1月6日搜查趙家賢的辦公。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n去年6月9日，梁晃維、 張可森及。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至7月6日戴耀廷、區諾軒及。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EUaBZr8FmUaoPj-ucMwVqO-1Qw4=/1000x3249/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZIB7A5DFFFFULN2DHALBS43SZ4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEUaBZr8FmUaoPj-ucMwVqO-1Qw4%3D%2F1000x3249%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZIB7A5DFFFFULN2DHALBS43SZ4.gif&h=477bdb54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dd69fb5219f65da45f100411db584aeb408599c","tid":2429343,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可是，控方無解釋，打算透過合法選舉取得議席，並且行使職權拒絕通過財政預算，如何構成顛覆國家政權行為，或有何法律理據。</blockquote>仲講法律理據？瞓咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c026787b6b9cd50b3721cbdb53ba414a87ae3ee","tid":2429343,"uid":93784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T08:43:39.000Z","msg":"算吧啦 意思係話基本法違反左國安法<br />\n證明左 中國法律 同 普通法 係完全矛盾同衝突嘅存在<br />\n只係中共權力迫使香港撕爛基本法同一國兩制姐"}]}